title: Health Tips with a Splash of Awkward

description:
Friday 1/13- Today's show consist of healthy tips with our good friend Dr. Oz and with a splash of some awkwardness from new comer Kodak Black even tho with the ski mask we were not quiet sure it was him. Also, Charlamagne awards a 12 year- old student for Donkey of the Day after trying to rob his classmate for a one chicken nugget.
